{"tid":710584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夾心階層，置業困難","createTime":"2018-06-21T01:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:28:16.000Z","uid":16284,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bebe224dfbdeeedb5596e4ca6058727494898544","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"月入33k<br />\n<br />\n公屋唔關我事<br />\n居屋又唔關我事<br />\n白居二又唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n無父幹無母幹，要搵層400萬內既盤只係得番啲單幢式40年樓齡既樓。比較新既就納米樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企只係得未補地價買左既公屋，要加按又要抬舊錢兇黎仲要供埋呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩老已經一個退休，一個就退休，要郁呢層樓佢地就真係好無安全感。<br />\n<br />\n唯一既後悔就係八年前老豆退休份唔算大既退休金拎左黎裝修間屋。而定諗番，如果無裝修，一出黎做野就上車，果時仲有d 正常盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉屌，儲首期永遠都追唔上加幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n想兩個人供又毒撚無女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n生仔就絕對無打算，結婚就隨緣樂助<br />\n<br />\n我只係想要個細細地有正常生活空間既屋<br />\n<br />\n呻完，屌你老母香港正苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7465b85ed57aed336cdc4d1513777ec9d4ed040","tid":710584,"uid":164920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"只要提下自己美孚新邨都五十幾年樓，即刻覺得四十年樓無乜問題"},{"pid":"5728c7396525593a8ae05919f8b0e49c09a5a628","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7465b85ed57aed336cdc4d1513777ec9d4ed040","tid":710584,"uid":164920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"只要提下自己美孚新邨都五十幾年樓，即刻覺得四十年樓無乜問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"d 單幢式高樓齡最怕要夾錢搞乜搞乜，<br />\n月入都供撚左一半，仲要供養父母，到時要拎舊錢出黎真係改埋間屋做一樓一賣屎忽都唔掂"},{"pid":"d9296137f7aaf34a2ec5b7d989fc7866c45ceeb1","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa09cb30fc792f22801689a85968a1e2f9339d1","tid":710584,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:16:04.000Z","msg":"買咗公屋仲買樓,戇鳩?繼續同你父母住咪得囉"},{"pid":"4b3bd0671b859dc79bee666d7160ddc3c6b6f7d8","tid":710584,"uid":6211,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:28:16.000Z","msg":"一條友又唔係要組織家庭<br />\n置業關你咩事"},{"pid":"f6a866317177f2638b9056ac3aa02c618094ac19","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfa09cb30fc792f22801689a85968a1e2f9339d1","tid":710584,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:16:04.000Z","msg":"買咗公屋仲買樓,戇鳩?繼續同你父母住咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:46:05.000Z","msg":"我只係好彩同屋企人關係正常，先可以慢慢思考出黎住既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應埋另一位，唔組織家庭就唔可以自己一個住？<br />\n<br />\n雖則話無咁大個頭唔好戴咁大頂帽，但係政策所限，我呢d 夾心撚獨立出黎住，反而本身係公屋戶or 公屋租戶既仔女可以用綠表入居屋or 白居二買層正常樓。<br />\n<br />\n我只係呻兩頭唔到岸，搵得多少少就反而要繼續痴屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595eda0678e49324a6deb7e39396cbeaa49f808e","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a866317177f2638b9056ac3aa02c618094ac19","tid":710584,"uid":16284,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfa09cb30fc792f22801689a85968a1e2f9339d1","tid":710584,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2